{"tid":1885292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本神戶有醫院被盜約六千個口罩","createTime":"2020-02-18T07:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T09:14:59.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcc2e1e284027f19b3d1c2d712108089a2b63e7","tid":1885292,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"【共同社2月18日電】18日採訪日本神戶市中央區的神戶紅十字醫院獲悉，該院稱約六千個口罩被盜，已向兵庫縣警葺合警署報案。由於口罩作為武漢病毒對策需求高漲，偷竊有可能以出售為目的，該警署將作為盜竊案件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n　　據該醫院稱，被盜的是醫用&ldquo;外科口罩&rdquo;，價值4萬日元。此前放在4個紙箱內保管在院內倉庫裡，13日職員檢查之際發現口罩不見了，於17日報案。據稱倉庫通常上鎖。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/02/abf1ab3b988e.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F02%2Fabf1ab3b988e.html&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=c75507da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/02/abf1ab3b988e.html</a>"},{"pid":"87f0c1b923a46a0b61d430eea5a377970d67aaa0","tid":1885292,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔使偵探頭腦都知係某強大国家背後策劃"},{"pid":"98f9e37e7e44c8452d6a6fbec99deca6225b3a81","tid":1885292,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"世界因為支那而變得痴線"},{"pid":"47019338a469382c214026fe6d3fbfcbb977c74f","tid":1885292,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0rofDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0rofDR.jpg&h=a8654aa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cacb7fa00e50f1d3dfd4059bc5dd258b4df3fff1","tid":1885292,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNE1M7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNE1M7Y.jpg&h=05546633&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}